<paragraph id="9D02B65B1C75E74CDD28AC2A243D768A" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">
Avena 
<normalizedToken id="EDE377FA86810C188B7F984BD70FEF6D" originalValue="núda" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">nuda</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="A6CD0EB88F08BF784A83C20DE0F92AE1" originalValue="Höjer" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">Hoejer</normalizedToken>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="051A28B0DAD9BDA4AE57B9A6BBE9264E" pageId="null" pageNumber="299" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="F83217476BF1DBBA1F25EA00B87C1603" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">Nackt-Hafer</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
</taxonomicName>
<subSubSection id="89957E30BF9ECF4CF8095C31B0C732B1" pageId="null" pageNumber="299" type="description">
<paragraph id="83B6CF2F8F8AFDCC758F1CFEC41EE3BA" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">
Rispe allseitswendig. 
<normalizedToken id="9901A8D22E20BBEE21D25ABCE1EBFB7C" originalValue="Ährchen" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">Aehrchen</normalizedToken>
zur Reifezeit noch nicht zerfallend; 
<emphasis id="4FC510804C0EB10D638B180FD2FD8AE0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">
Deckspelzen mit senkrechter, zackig umrandeter Abbruchstelle. Deckspelzen kahl, zur Reifezeit von gleicher Beschaffenheit wie die 
<normalizedToken id="22E86A7031E3A722748C9E4041D669BA" originalValue="Hüllspelzen" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">Huellspelzen</normalizedToken>
: weich, die Frucht nicht 
<normalizedToken id="9A8204811DEBEBEC4B81B036FBE4F1D7" originalValue="umschlieβend" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">umschlieβend</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
, (bei allen andern Arten die Deckspelzen starr, die Frucht 
<normalizedToken id="9ADF030483E48C45F3F9DD4846B392C9" originalValue="umschließend" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">umschliessend</normalizedToken>
); Granne auf dem 
<normalizedToken id="CB8480DD612B1ED366FC397FAD7CD4B8" originalValue="Rücken" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">Ruecken</normalizedToken>
der Deckspelze oft kurz, 
<normalizedToken id="C31EBEA9B569878835C82EED1C9A18D9" originalValue="früh" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">frueh</normalizedToken>
abbrechend oder nicht vorhanden. - 
<normalizedToken id="98924EB674F5199E3F66123579DBE652" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="948D4603F769C2073944A27B29A4DAA5" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">
<emphasis id="02459C9EFA1D708809F3A3391A6364EB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">Zytologische Angaben. 2n = 14:</emphasis>
Zahlreiche 
<normalizedToken id="894C1205CB8AC9DCD4C04CC200D24B77" originalValue="übereinstimmende" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">uebereinstimmende</normalizedToken>
Angaben in 
<normalizedToken id="0DAC1C6F19CA49AC1BC7667C68F29BBA" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">Loeve</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="CEA7A41B2BAF5F3C8DB27BFD20CE0C66" originalValue="LövE" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">LoevE</normalizedToken>
. (1961).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5FD88E0C012FBC00EB4AC4A44B6C0A37" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">
<emphasis id="238463C5F51BFF99F08303651B789FE6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">Standort.</emphasis>
Wie 
<taxonomicName id="2065B804FF5A28D653B3DACACE922A20" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Avena" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="299" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sativa">
<emphasis id="683D4280A42BB7C3BD14CF6C034B508F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">A. sativa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 5). Als Ackerunkraut gelegentlich mit 
<taxonomicName id="C7F10F1BF21738E10FC77968ED340D48" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Avena" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="299" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sativa">
<emphasis id="24FC8729ADA106107CF533923B98A431" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">A. sativa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
zusammen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BF8A8DAFEEE165C2A0C9ED62C0B44C2E" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">
<emphasis id="8B7A61B40283D5885854A2E60893F429" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">Verbreitung.</emphasis>
Wie 
<taxonomicName id="F6117C0E54F1391016A4643517DBFE4C" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Avena" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="299" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sativa">
<emphasis id="B93D284F8B91DB163E9AC4257C3003F4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">A. sativa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 5).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
